==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Adonist
<hw>A*do"nist</hw> <pr>(⟦adot⟧*d⟦omac⟧"n⟦icr⟧st)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Heb. <ets>⟦acr⟧d⟦omac⟧n⟦amac⟧i</ets> my Lords.]</ety> <def>One who
maintains that points of the Hebrew word translated
⟦ldquo⟧Jehovah⟦rdquo⟧ are really the vowel points of the word
⟦ldquo⟧Adonai.⟦rdquo⟧ See <er>Jehovist</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Adonize</ent>⟦br⟧
